\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">2차로는 길건너에 있는</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">\"PLZEN\" 이라는 맥주집으로 갔어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/387df0c99f3fbba4.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfMjQ5/MDAxNTE3NTU1OTE2ODQ4.E4WQi9afi0pjbmqQ8g5OI27hO8B4W31IaZg3VDpJM4Ag.vhV6vEfHK0kShfy75BnkiRR29UykkrfQzJPYwghORokg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180202_155720438.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000338086E085')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/387df0c99f3fbba4.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">여기 장식품이 무슨...</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">외국에 있는.. 그 뭐냐.. 뭐라고 하지</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/403ccc5a3d3b0586.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfNjkg/MDAxNTE3N