px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfNzcg/MDAxNTE3NTU1OTE3MTgw.3Jf-4zVd75jO5udH44R3MC4ICvw8LU68T-k7VrTTaKwg.M0RQ76Ni4FUKjUquAbxlWQiysukpGQiMpdLhclKgOTAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180202_155719838.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000338086E085')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3e1100d8bfeef7f8.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">이거 우리원장님이 좋아하시는 먹태</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1fcd7f5b4ad13f7e.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfMTA0/MDAxNTE3NTU1OTE3Mjgx.bL2rvclAMSAbFs-HhEtiMWx48UobRN8XSCBoZQczWOMg.fffEWtdpVphAvzBklx5zYMKywD8dii-V6JQztB-PKXsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180202_155719985.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000338086E085')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1fcd7f5b4ad13f7e.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">먹기 좋게 또 잘라주셨어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5ef15b9a3814ca07.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfMjE4/MDAxNTE3NTU1OTE3NDIz.1iKGBm89JJ1Nlmh3Qm232MbJDfU6kJJ1Ezh41Bc8DEgg.5m2IIABUTTTXZ2FbuAKYJB0DLTncGVnEB35JgA8jH0cg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180202_155720235.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000338086E085')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5ef15b9a3814ca07.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">이거는 쭈삼겹볶음 이었나?</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">귀여운 쭈꾸미가 통체로 들어있어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">그것도 많이</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">고기도 많고 야채도 많고</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16b67b0b1502c39b.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMDJfMTQ1/MDAxNTE3NTU1OTE3NTIz.noKLhGInfsi0ZhZtEql9dXtPaC7kOoMXtyPitcxJdqwg.eWOrfsHu8hRxCgKUYAAAiHToF0kC7fe7nCfi-P4z3qUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180202_155719695.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000338086E085')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16b67b0b1502c39b.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">저는 오렌지 쥬스</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64e9b72df78c6cf4.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-35\"></a><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">이번 회식 진짜 너무 재밌었어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">젊고 어리고 이쁜 알바샘덕에 술게임도 해보고</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">우리 원장님 두분 모두 즐거워보이셨어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">이런 회식 매일 했으면 좋겠네요&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">매일 퇴근하고 회식하러 가...면 원장님 지갑 빵꾸 나겠죠?</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">ㅎㅎㅎ</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\">새로오신 우리 가지샘 환영해요!!!</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 굴림, Gulim;\">우리 힘을 합쳐서 열심히 잘 해보아요~&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">암튼 2018년 한해는 우리 이수한의원 식구들&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">모두 건강하고 아프지않고</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">기쁘고 </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림, Gulim; font-size: 14pt;\">좋은일만 생겼으면 좋겠어요</span></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
